# KinoProgressBar

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:kino_progress_bar, "~> 0.1"}
])
```

## Progress bar

```elixir
progress_bar = KinoProgressBar.new("PROGRESS")
```

```elixir
KinoProgressBar.set_current(progress_bar, 20)
```

```elixir
red_bar = KinoProgressBar.new(
  "Red",
  color: :red,
  width: 800,
  range: {0, 1000},
  current: 500,
  format_current: fn index -> "#{index} å›ž" end,
  throttle: 100
)
```

```elixir
0..1000
|> Enum.each(fn index ->
  Process.sleep(2)
  KinoProgressBar.set_current(red_bar, index)
end)
```
